@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mt-6">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md mt-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-4">1. Introduction</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600">
        Welcome to <strong>StudentMind</strong>. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your personal information when you participate in our program.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600">
        <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email, student ID.</li>
        <li><strong>Survey Responses:</strong> Answers to surveys, choices selected, and scores.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Log data, browser type, IP address, and interactions.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600">
        <li>Provide and improve our program’s services.</li>
        <li>Analyze survey responses for well-being insights.</li>
        <li>Generate anonymized reports for research.</li>
        <li>Communicate with participants regarding their surveys.</li>
        <li>Ensure compliance with legal requirements.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-4">4. Data Protection & Security</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600">
        We implement encryption, restricted access, and regular audits to protect your data. However, no data transmission over the internet is 100% secure.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-4">5. Data Retention</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600">
        We retain data only as long as necessary. Users may request data access, correction, or deletion by contacting us.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-4">6. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600">
        We may use third-party tools for analytics, hosting, or communication. These services have their own privacy policies.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-4">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600">
        We may update this policy periodically. Continued use of our services after updates constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-4">8. Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600">
        📧 <strong>Email:</strong> studentmind@fpt.edu.vn <br />
        📞 <strong>Phone:</strong> 0123456789 <br />
        🏢 <strong>Address:</strong> 123, Hung Vuong, Phu Nhuan, Thu Duc, Ho Chi Minh
    </p>
</div>
